2015-03-21 15:09:28 : Stop, Loop and file check added.
2015-03-18 18:48:58 : Load Wav file added.

Usage : 

SoundManager sound_manager(1);                  // Number of sound file to load
ALuint sound = sound_manager.load("sound.wav"); // #include <AL/al.h> for ALuint
sound_manager.play(sound);

